         <h4>Born </h4>
         <h4>Died </h4>
         <h4>Bio: </h4>
         <p>
            Elizabeth Gaskell, the author of the journal, was born in 1810 and died in
            1865. She published her first novel, Mary Barton, in
            1848, and later became a successful novelist.Elizabeth Gaskell, the author of the journal, was born in 1810 and died in
            1865. She published her first novel, Mary BartonMary Barton, in
