      <div class="persRef" id="Hannah_Holland_Lumb">
         
         <h4><span class="forename">Hannah</span><span class="givenName">Holland</span><span class="marriedName">Lumb</span></h4>
         <h4>Born </h4>
         <h4>Died </h4>
         <h4>Bio: </h4>
         <p>
            Hannah Lumb was the sister of Elizabeth (Holland) Stevenson, Elizabeth Gaskell's mother.
            After Elizabeth Stevenson’s death when Elizabeth was only 13 months old,, Hannah Lumb
            and her daughter,
            Marianne, took Gaskell to live with them in Knutsford. Marianne died shortly
            after, and Gaskell lived with Aunt Lumb until her marrriage. Hannah Lumb was the sister of Elizabeth (Holland) Stevenson, Elizabeth Gaskell's mother.
            After Elizabeth Stevenson’s death when Elizabeth was only 13 months old,, Hannah Lumb
            and her daughter,
            Marianne, took Gaskell to live with them in Knutsford. Marianne died shortly
            after, and Gaskell lived with Aunt Lumb until her marrriage. 
            </p>
         
         
         
         
         
         
         
         Hannah Lumb was the sister of Elizabeth (Holland) Stevenson, Elizabeth Gaskell's mother.
         After Elizabeth Stevenson’s death when Elizabeth was only 13 months old,, Hannah Lumb
         and her daughter,
         Marianne, took Gaskell to live with them in Knutsford. Marianne died shortly
